  [Text] Pyongyang, March 15 (KCNA) -- A group of inspectors 
of the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA) left here today 
[15 March] by air after visiting Korea for an inspection to 
ensure continuity of safeguards according to the agreement 
between the DPRK and the United States. 

