<H3> <TI>   Koreans in Japan Denounce Waste Dumping </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1303084394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0830 GMT 13 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1303084394 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tokyo, March 11 (KNS-KCNA) -- The Central Standing 
Committee of the General Association of Korean Residents in 
Japan (Chongnyon) released a statement on March 11 denouncing 
the criminal act of the South Korean authorities in dumping 
nuclear waste in the East Sea of Korea at random. 
  The statement branded the nuclear waste dumping by the Kim 
Yong-sam clique as the heaviest anti-national crime of turning 
Korea into a barren land polluted with nuclear substances and 
cutting off the lifeline of the nation and as a wanton violation 
of international law and convention. 
  The statement further said: 
  The traitorous Kim Yong-sam group which, while developing 
nuclear weapons under the "nuclear umbrella" of the United 
States, had cried for "an international cooperation system" and 
"a military countermeasure" and now, even at the working contact 
for the exchange of special envoys between the two parts of 
Korea, is reversing the black and white, raising a row over the 
"nuclear issue". This is outrageous, indeed. 
  To make the matter worse, the traitor Kim Yong-sam plans to 
visit Japan a few days later and have a confab for a more 
vicious smear campaign against the DPRK and Chongnyon. This 
will be a criminal mendicant trip designed to balk the 
projected third round of DPRK-U.S. talks at any cost in 
conspiracy with outside forces and continue to do harm to the 
DPRK. 
  The Kim Yong-sam clique has been hell bent on flunkeyist 
treachery, fascism, confrontation with the North and splittist 
moves and, as if it were not enough, is now unhesitatingly 
dumping radioactive waste. This is a criminal act which can be 
committed only by them who are clean indifferent to the nation 
and international law. 
  The South Korean rulers must stop the criminal nuclear waste 
dumping at once, disclose its truth and apologize to the whole 
nation. 
  We strongly demand that the Kim Yong-sam regime immediately 
give up the anti-reunification and anti-national moves to kill 
fellow countrymen in reliance upon outside forces, scrap the 
"National Security Law" and unconditionally stop the fascist 
suppression of the South Korean people. 

</TEXT>

