<H3> <TI>   Kim Il-song Sends Wreath to Bier of Late Actor </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK1303090494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0848 GMT 13 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1303090494 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 13 (KCNA) -- The great leader 
President Kim Il-song sent a wreath to the bier of the late 
people's actor Han Chin-sop of the state theatrical company, 
expressing deep sorrow over his death. 
  Han Chin-sop died of illness at the age of 79 on March 12. 
He dedicated his all to the work for the development of 
literature and art, upholding the literary and art idea and line 
of the Workers' Party of Korea. 

</TEXT>

