Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An Indonesian fishing boat has been apprehended by 
the Australian Navy near Christmas Island in the Indian Ocean. 
The boat with 13 crew was spotted near the island yesterday by 
the Broome-based coast watch aircraft. It is alleged the 
longline vessel was fishing illegally in Australian waters. 
