<DOCNO> FBIS3-6298 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas051_a_94010" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-051 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  16 Mar 1994 </DATE1>

