<F P=101> Burma </F>
<H3> <TI>   Calls on Development Minister </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK1603160894 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 16 Mar 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK1603160894 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>


<TEXT>
