<F P=103> SK1703043294 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 17 (KCNA) -- The U.S. imperialists, 
on March 15, staged an exercise of returning to the base after 
dropping bombs in the air above Yongwol and Pyongchang, South 
Korea, with the mobilization of Japan-based F-15 fighter-bombers 
and FA-18 pursuit-assault planes, according to military sources. 
  On the 14th and the 15th, overseas-based KC-135s refueled 
more than 30 fighter-bombers and assault planes in an air war 
exercise above Kunsan and Kapyong. 
  Meanwhile the Kim Yong-sam group staged a war rehearsal on 
the 15th with the mobilization of many warships, attack 
helicopters, artillery pieces, tanks and armoured vehicles. 
  At that time, a "civilian defence training" was under way in 
Seoul. 
  The U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppets would be 
well advised to act with discretion, clearly mindful of the 
grave consequences to be entailed by their reckless belligerent 
moves increasing tension on the Korean peninsula. 

