<F P=106> ["Only Grave Awaits `Civilian President'" -- KCNA headline] </F>
  [Text] Pyongyang, March 17 (KCNA) -- Only the grave awaits 
the traitor Kim Yong-sam, a "civilian president" forsaken and 
rejected by the people for his anti-national, anti-popular 
crimes, says NODONG SINMUN in an article today. 
  The author of the article says: 
  The traitor Kim Yong-sam and his "civilian" regime are 
destined to meet a miserable doom. The puppet Kim Young-sam had 
been a target of hatred among the people before he took the 
"presidential" seat as a thorough-paced traitor and turncoat. 
