<H5>  Revival of Hosokawa Support Rate </H5>
  The support rate for the Hosokawa cabinet sharply declined 
in 
the December survey, but it picked up by 3 percent in January. 
It appears Prime Minister Hosokawa's 14 December decision on a 
partial rice liberalization left no obvious impact on the 
support rate. Prime Minister Hosokawa managed the rice issue, 
but future development of the political scene is still uncertain 
as the upper house rejected the political reform bills. 


------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Table 3. Public Support for Opposition Leaders                               | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Date                     |support rate (%)         |remarks                  | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
