<F P=100> ANNEX </F>
<F P=101> Japan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Poll Details Support Rates for Cabinet, Parties </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1503151894 Tokyo CHUO KORON in Japanese Apr 94 pp 74-75 -- 
FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW1503151894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo CHUO KORON </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Japanese </F>
