<H5>  Pollees' Voting Intentions </H5>
  The top three popular parties were the LDP, the JNP, and the 
SDPJ. Compared with the January survey, support for Shinseito 
dropped by 2 percent. 
  NOTE: The survey, conducted by Chuo Research Inc. on 10-13 
February, was carried on as individual interviews of 2,000 
eligible voters picked at random. Responses were obtained from 
68.1 percent of, or 1,361, pollees. Data belong to the 
Multipurpose Statistic Databank of Tsukuba University. 

